    "photographerNetwork": "Nearly 50 photographers, retouchers and visual specialists can be coordinated for selected projects.",
    "coordination": "Project coordination depends on project requirements: Norbert Banhalmi, a dedicated BANHALMI team coordinator, or for selected AmCham-related international business projects, Speier Viko.",
    "amChamBenefit": "AmCham members can receive 50% more professionally retouched images than selected, at no additional cost."
